label lb_w3eow_police_hotel:
    # Week 3 (EOW) Scene 04 - Police come to the hotel to investigate"
    scene sc w3eowpolice p01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/03/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" loop fadein 1.0
    s"Why on earth are all these police officers here?"
    mc"(Oh no‚Ä¶ This doesn‚Äôt look good at all.)"
    # (S approaches a police officer, who is the Seaside chief of police)"
    show sc w3eowpolice p04
    s"Excuse me, Sir, can I ask what you‚Äôre doing here?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p02
    chi"This is a police matter, Miss. It doesn‚Äôt concern you."
    show sc w3eowpolice p05
    s"Well I‚Äôm pretty sure it does because you and your officers are blocking the entrance to my hotel!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p02
    chi"This is your hotel?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p05
    s"Yes it is! Now can you please explain to me what the hell is going on here?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p03
    chi"I‚Äôm sorry miss but we have a warrant to search the premises of your hotel for a missing person."
    show sc w3eowpolice p06
    mc"A missing person? Who?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p07
    chi"It‚Äôs this young lady."
    # (The chief shows her a picture of Connie)"
    chi"Her name is Connie, and it is understood that she was here yesterday."
    mc"Oh..."
    show sc w3eowpolice p02
    chi"Were you here yesterday Miss?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p04
    s"No I wasn‚Äôt."
    show sc w3eowpolice p06
    chi"How about you Sir? Were you here? Did you see this girl?"
    mc"Uh, yes I was but no, I haven‚Äôt seen this girl."
    show sc w3eowpolice p08
    chi"Well, we have a witness who saw her leave with a young male and a young female yesterday afternoon in a car from this hotel."
    chi"Are you sure that‚Äôs the story that you want to go with Sir?"
    mc"Yes, I‚Äôm positive."
    mc"Do you mind if we see this warrant, officer? I've studied law and we're well within our rights to request and also sight this warrant."
    show sc w3eowpolice p04
    s"I'd like to see this warrant too."
    show sc w3eowpolice p08
    chi"Yes, of course."
    chi"Just give me a couple of minutes to get it for you."
    mc"May I ask who this witness was?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p09
    lu"That witness would be me."
    show sc w3eowpolice p10
    s"(Oh my God, it‚Äôs him.)"
    show sc w3eowpolice p11
    mc"You? You‚Äôre the witness?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p12
    lu"Yeah, and I caught you red-handed asshole!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p08
    mc"Officer, I found this guy snooping around the hotel grounds yesterday."
    mc"He was on private property, and you shouldn‚Äôt believe a word out of his mouth."
    chi"I‚Äôm sorry folks, but as I said, we have a search warrant to check the hotel."
    show sc w3eowpolice p05
    s"On what grounds?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p09
    lu"On the grounds that her father is looking for her. Connie is now regarded as a missing person, and you and your hotel are the prime suspects!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p05
    s"This is complete bullshit! This douche attacked me in broad daylight a couple of weeks ago officer."
    show sc w3eowpolice p02
    chi"Did you report this alleged incident ma‚Äôam?"
    show sc w3eowpolice p04
    s"I uh. No, no I didn‚Äôt."
    show sc w3eowpolice p02
    chi"Well I‚Äôm sorry, but there‚Äôs nothing I can do about that."
    chi"This girl‚Äôs father has used all his resources to find his daughter..."
    chi"And due to the seriousness of the matter, and the fact that she‚Äôs been missing for more than twenty-four hours..."
    show sc w3eowpolice p03
    chi"I‚Äôm authorised to tell you that your hotel will need to be shut down temporarily until it has been thoroughly checked over."
    show sc w3eowpolice p05
    s"No! You can‚Äôt! I have a business to run! And we have guests to attend to!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p03
    chi"The few guests that were staying here have already been asked to leave the premises."
    chi"The hotel is now completely vacated."
    show sc w3eowpolice p12
    lu"Hahaha!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p13
    with vpunch
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w3eowpolice p13b","v_rewards_s_38")
    play sound "sound effects/03/01/Punch_Sound_Effect.mp3"
    s"You son of a bitch!"
    # (S takes a swing at Lucas and hits him in the face)"
    # (Punch sound effect)"
    lu"OW!!"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w3eowpolice p14
    mc"(Oh [s_name]! What have you done?)"
    lu"Did you see that officer? She assaulted me!"
    chi"Officers, please take the lady into custody."
    s"What? You can‚Äôt!"
    show sc w3eowpolice p15
    mc"You bastard! You won‚Äôt get away with this!"
    lu"Hehe, looks like I already did."
    # (Lucas whispers in the MC‚Äôs ear)"
    show sc w3eowpolice p16
    lu"Now I got you and that bitch right where I want you‚Ä¶"
    mc"(Okay, I‚Äôve had enough of this jackass!)"
    # (The MC takes a swing at Lucas and punches him in the gut)"
