            s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder why he did that for?)"
            show sc w3eowpolice p68
            s"Oh, well, you know you could‚Äôve slept in my bed while I was away?"
            show sc w3eowpolice p66
            mc"I would have done, but, [c_name] stayed the night as well so I let her sleep in your bed."
            mc"I wasn‚Äôt sure when you were coming home and I thought it would be a good idea to sleep on the sofa, just in case you returned home."
            mc"That way you‚Äôd definitely see me."
            show sc w3eowpolice p70
            show screen scr_rewards("sc w3eowpolice p70b","v_rewards_s_39")
            s"(That makes sense. And it was nice of [y_name] to give up the two beds.)"
            hide screen scr_rewards
            show sc w3eowpolice p66
            s"May I ask, is there any reason why you didn‚Äôt put Connie up in one of the hotel rooms?"
            mc"I wasn‚Äôt sure if I should, or if you would be okay with that."
            mc"I mean, you hadn‚Äôt met her yet and [c_name] and I had only known her for a few hours."
            mc"At least if she was staying in my room, then I could keep a close eye on her."
            show sc w3eowpolice p68
            s"I see‚Ä¶"
            show sc w3eowpolice p70
            s"(I think he‚Äôs telling the truth.)"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            s"(He could‚Äôve easily lied to me and I would‚Äôve been none the wiser.)" #+2 S POINTS"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3eowpolice p66
    mc"Anyway, give me a second here to call Trisha."
    mc"Once we know what‚Äôs happening with the hotel, then we can start making plans for the rest of the day."
    show sc w3eowpolice p68
