    tri"The police haven‚Äôt found any evidence of any wrongdoing so you and [s_name] should be okay to head back there in an hour or two."
    tri"I‚Äôll confirm this to you both as soon as I find out."
    show sc w3eowpolice p71
    mc"Terrific, thank you so much Trisha. I honestly don‚Äôt know how to repay you."

    if v_day3_trisha_website:
        # ‚ÄúTrisha path (if the player has seen her sexy photos)‚Äù"
