                show sc w3eowroshi r13
                ro"No problem. Roshi want you to keep."
                show sc w3eowroshi r12
                mc"Oh no, that‚Äôs way too generous."
                mc"Besides, I‚Äôm not sure if I‚Äôll be staying in Sunshine Bay after the summer ends, so I could end up having to give it back to you."
                ro"We shall see."
                jump lb_w3eow_roshi_elevator_menu
            else:
                # ‚ÄúAdd lines if the MC did not go flying with Yuki‚Äù"
