    mc"I think you should definitely ask her."
    mc"Maybe there are things she wants to do or to try but she doesn‚Äôt know how to ask you."
    mc"Or she may not think that you would understand. "
    show sc w3eowroshi r17
    ro"Roshi will consider."
    # (MC smiles)"
