    ro"Thank you [y_name] san for your help."
    mc"Oh, you‚Äôre welcome Mister Roshi."
    mc"(I don‚Äôt think I did that much but it‚Äôs great to be able to listen and to learn from him.)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
