label lb_w3eow_kristina_call:
    # Week 3 (EOW) Scene 10 - Kristina calls the MC, reminding him about helping her that night"
    scene sc w3eowroshi r32
    with dissolve
    mc"(All right, now that that‚Äôs sorted...)"
    mc"(I should have enough time to clean up the pool area before [s_name] returns.)"
    mc"(We have so much to do between now and when Connie‚Äôs party starts tomorrow, and with no guests staying in the hotel at the moment, time shouldn‚Äôt be an issue.)"
    # (phone call sound FX)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_Phone_Ring_Sound_Effect.mp3" loop
    mc"(Oh!)"
    mc"(That‚Äôs probably [s_name] calling me now.)"
    # (MC pulls out his phone, sees Kristina calling him)"
    mc"(Oh, hang on a minute, it‚Äôs [k_name]! I wonder why she‚Äôs calling me?)"
    # (MC answers it)"
    stop sound
    mc"Good afternoon, this is [y_name]."
    # (show Kristina on the other end of the phone line - maybe only wearing a towel so she looks hot without giving too much away)"
    show sc w3eowroshi r37
    k"Hey [y_name], it‚Äôs [k_name]. How are you?"
    mc"I‚Äôm great thanks. Yourself?"
    show sc w3eowroshi r35
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w3eowroshi r35","sc w3eowroshi r35x","v_pt_image_index_w3_33")
    k"I‚Äôve been great as well."
    k"What have you been up to?"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w3eowroshi r32
    mc"[s_name] and I have had a hell of a week since I last saw you on the day of the wedding, and we also have another function booked in for tomorrow."
    k"That‚Äôs great [y_name]!"
    show sc w3eowroshi r37
    k"I‚Äôm really happy for you both."
    show sc w3eowroshi r36
    k"But I hope that doesn‚Äôt mean that you‚Äôre not going to be free tonight."
    # [Tonight? / I sure am]"
    show sc w3eowroshi r32
    menu:
        "Tonight?":
            mc"Uhh‚Ä¶ Tonight?"
            show sc w3eowroshi r35
            $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,-2,k_name)
            k"Yes, you agreed to meet with me this evening to see if my father is up to anything suspicious at the church, remember?" #-2 KRISTINA POINTS"
            show sc w3eowroshi r32
            mc"(Fuck!! I forgot all about it.)"
            mc"(Damn, I can‚Äôt cancel my plans with [k_name] now, not when I‚Äôm supposed to meet with her tonight.)"
            mc"R-right‚Ä¶ I remember."
            mc"So uh, what time shall I meet you, and where?"
        "I sure am"(wt="Best choice"):
            mc"No, I‚Äôm still meeting with you this evening [k_name]."
            show sc w3eowroshi r37
            k"Awesome! I thought for a moment that you may have forgotten."
            mc"Not at all."
            show sc w3eowroshi r32
            $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,2,k_name)
            mc"It‚Äôs obviously important and I did promise that I'd be joining you tonight." # +2 KRISTINA POINTS"
            mc"So what time shall I meet you, and where?"
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3eowroshi r35
    k"I was thinking around six o‚Äôclock, around sunset."
    k"That will give us enough time to go over the plan before we head to the church."
    show sc w3eowroshi r37
    k"Why don‚Äôt you meet me at my house?"
    show sc w3eowroshi r35
    k"My Mom won‚Äôt be home until after we leave so it should be okay."
    show sc w3eowroshi r32
    mc"Oh‚Ä¶ Sure thing, I guess I can do that."
    k"Okay, I‚Äôll text you my address shortly."
    show sc w3eowroshi r37
    k"I‚Äôll see you in a few hours [y_name]. Bye."
    show sc w3eowroshi r32
    mc"Bye [k_name]."
    # (call ends)"
    mc"(Shit! How on earth am I going to explain to [s_name] that I have to go out for a couple of hours this evening?)"
    mc"(I haven‚Äôt had any time to even think about what I‚Äôll say to her, ever since I made this agreement with [k_name].)"
    mc"(And what's [s_name] going to think when, or if I tell her that I‚Äôll be spending this evening with someone else?)"
    mc"(Maybe this time I should just tell her the truth.)"
    mc"([s_name] may not completely understand why I‚Äôm doing this after I explain it to her, but I made a promise to [k_name].)"
    mc"(And I‚Äôm not breaking that promise.)"
    mc"(Even I‚Äôm more than intrigued to find out what her father could be involved in at the church.)"
    mc"(The least I can do is make sure that the hotel and the pool area are as tidy and presentable as possible before [s_name] returns.)"
    mc"(That way, I‚Äôm not leaving her with too much to do here at the hotel.)"
    mc"(The rest of the work will mainly be setting things up before the start of tomorrow‚Äôs party‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)







label lb_w3eow_mc_k_ready:
    #     Week 3 (EOW) Scene 11 - MC gets ready for his night with Kristina"
    scene sc w3eowkdate1 k01
    with dissolve
    mc"(I hope what I‚Äôm wearing is okay.)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k02
    mc"(It probably doesn‚Äôt matter too much because as far as I remember, [k_name] is expecting me to wear a priest‚Äôs outfit!)"
    mc"(Which means I‚Äôll have to enter the church at some point, more than likely.)"
    mc"(I wonder where [s_name] is? She should‚Äôve been back by now.)"
    mc"(Surely she hasn‚Äôt gone missing again? Not the night before her hotel is hosting another event.)"
    mc"(I don‚Äôt want to leave here without telling her where I‚Äôm going.)"
    mc"(At the same time, I don‚Äôt want to be late to meet up with [k_name] either.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôll give [s_name] another fifteen minutes, and if she hasn‚Äôt returned, then I‚Äôll call her to see where she is‚Ä¶)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (MC waits in the living room)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3eowkdate1 k03
    with dissolve
    mc"(Dammit‚Ä¶ I can‚Äôt wait around any longer for [s_name].)"
    mc"(I‚Äôll give her a call, but if she doesn‚Äôt answer then I‚Äôm going to have to leave.)"
    # (MC takes his phone out, and just as he‚Äôs about to call, S bursts through the door)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k05
    s"[y_name]! Hey! I‚Äôm so sorry I took so long."
    s"After going to the mall I had to go and see Ivy and Lily so the three of us could properly plan out tomorrow‚Äôs party."
    s"We had to order a few more things and I completely lost track of time."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"It‚Äôs fine [s_name]. I was just about to call you."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k07
    s"Well I‚Äôm here now, and once I put everything away, I can make some dinner for us if you‚Äôd like me to?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"Um‚Ä¶"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k09
    s"Hey, what are you all dressed up for? Are you going somewhere?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"Uh, yes I am. I have plans for the night."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k05
    s"Plans? What plans?"
    mc"Okay, here‚Äôs the truth."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"When [k_name] was here last Saturday morning to decorate the events room, I promised that I would help her out with something."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    s"And what is this something?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"It‚Äôs at the church, her father‚Äôs church."
    s"Why would you want to go with [k_name] to her father‚Äôs church?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k10
    s"Wait! You‚Äôre not going to become one of them, are you??"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"Haha, no, that‚Äôs not why I‚Äôm going."
    mc"[k_name] suspects that her father is doing something illegal or maybe even immoral..."
    mc"And she asked for my help to find some evidence to clear him of any wrongdoing."
    s"But why you?"
    mc"I guess she didn‚Äôt really know who else to ask."
    mc"And when [k_name] asked for my help, I thought it was the least I could do after she offered to work for us for free."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k09
    s"(Hmm... Sometimes [y_name] is way too nice.)"
    s"(But on the other hand, it‚Äôs hard for me to be angry with him at the same time.)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k05
    s"Do you have to go with her tonight, of all nights? I mean, we have a party to prepare for tomorrow, remember?"
    mc"I know, but I just need to go and do this. I‚Äôll be back before you know it."
    s"How long do you think you will be?"
    mc"A couple of hours at most. I guess it depends on if we find anything or not."
    mc"But as soon as we‚Äôre done, then I promise I‚Äôll come straight back here to help you with the party."
    # (MC holds S‚Äô hands)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    mc"Please, just trust me with this [s_name], okay?"
    s"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    s"All right‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm sure I can take care of a few things while you‚Äôre out."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    s"Did you at least get the service elevator repaired with Mister Roshi?"
    mc"Yep, it‚Äôs working properly again. However, we had a bit of a problem."
    mc"Mister Roshi almost collapsed and he asked me to call his nurse. An ambulance arrived and took him to the hospital."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k10
    s"Oh my God! Is he okay?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k05
    mc"It seemed like he was."
    mc"He was complaining about having chest pains but then he seemed as if he was in good spirits when his nurse arrived."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k06
    s"Damn‚Ä¶ I never should have asked him to fix the elevator. I should‚Äôve called someone else to do it."
    s"And I should have been here for him."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    s"I presume that Yuki knows about this?"
    mc"No, Mister Roshi asked me not to tell Yuki, as he didn‚Äôt want her to worry."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder why he didn‚Äôt want [y_name] to tell Yuki. She has a right to know when her father is in hospital.)"
    if v_w2_k_yuki_plane_lessons:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player is on the Yuki path‚Äù"
        show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
        mc"I think Mister Roshi wants me to spend some time with Yuki to maybe help to take her mind off her father‚Äôs health issues."
        mc"It sounds like it‚Äôs really bothering her and he asked me if I could take her out sometime..."
        mc"Just so she can focus on something else for a few hours I guess."
        mc"Would that be okay if I were to do that sometime soon?"
        show sc w3eowkdate1 k07
        s"Yes, of course you can, it‚Äôs completely understandable."
        show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
        s"But would it just be you and Yuki?"
        mc"Oh, well, he didn‚Äôt say. Perhaps you could come with me?"
        show sc w3eowkdate1 k07
        s"Sure, I‚Äôd love to."
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k04
    mc"Anyway, I really need to get going. I presume you'll be awake when I get back?"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k07
    s"I might be tired but I need to get through it, as I have plenty of setting up to do for tomorrow."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    s"It‚Äôs been a very long day, especially after leaving the beach house, then being arrested, then being let out of jail‚Ä¶"
    s"And then spending most of my afternoon with the twins."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k07
    s"I guess it serves me right for disappearing for a few days, huh?"
    mc"Haha, probably."
    # (S hugs the MC)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k06
    s"Just promise me that you‚Äôll take care of yourself and you won‚Äôt do anything silly. I know what that church can be like."
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k05
    mc"I‚Äôll do what I can."
    mc"Bye [s_name]. I‚Äôll be right back."
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    s"(I hope so‚Ä¶)"
    # (MC leaves)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k09
    s"(I wonder why [y_name] didn‚Äôt mention anything about this night out with [k_name] earlier?)"
    s"(I mean, he‚Äôs known about it for nearly a week. Did it just slip his mind?)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k08
    s"(Then again, he hasn‚Äôt seen me for nearly four days, any maybe that could be a reason why he didn‚Äôt tell me until now.)"
    s"(Oh my God! Why am I acting like a jealous girlfriend??)"
    s"(I did this with Connie, then [c_name], and now [k_name]!)"
    s"(Aside from [c_name], he hardly knows the other two girls.)"
    show sc w3eowkdate1 k11
