    mc"I ended up running into the back of a parked car!"
    show sc w3eowscooter c11
    s"Oh my God! Were you okay?"
    show sc w3eowscooter c09
    mc"No‚Ä¶ I had several stitches and I also broke my left arm."
    show sc w3eowscooter c08
    mc"I resented my Dad for letting go when I told him not to, and I was too scared to hop on a bike again after that day."
    show sc w3eowscooter c09
    s"Oh [y_name]. I‚Äôm so sorry, I had no idea."
    mc"I‚Äôve never told anyone that before."
    show sc w3eowscooter c08
    mc"That‚Äôs why I was so reluctant to drive when you took me into town for dinner the night after I got here."
    mc"I didn‚Äôt want you to know about my fear."
    # (MC looks down)"
    # (S lays his hands upon his)"
    show sc w3eowscooter c09
    s"Hey‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs okay, we all have fears, things that worry us."
    s"You know you can talk to me about anything, right [y_name]? I won‚Äôt judge, I just want to help."
    mc"Thanks [s_name]."
    show sc w3eowscooter c08
    s"So, do you still wanna give it another try?"
    show sc w3eowscooter c07
