        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w3eowscooter c07","sc w3eowscooter c07x","v_pt_image_index_w3_35")
    s"I promise I won‚Äôt let go of you."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w3eowscooter c08
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ I‚Äôve been putting this off since I got here.)"
    mc"(I guess if I don‚Äôt want to have to keep walking to get anywhere in this town then I need to learn how to do this.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm not six years old anymore, so I have no excuses really.)"
    mc"I want to at least give it a try."
    show sc w3eowscooter c10
    s"Great!"
    show sc w3eowscooter c07
    mc"All right, I have my helmet on. What now?"
    show sc w3eowscooter c10
    s"Hop on! I‚Äôll sit behind you and give you some instructions."
