    # (MC sits on the scooter)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3eowscooter c12
    with dissolve
    s"Now let me just get comfortable here."
    # (S sits on the scooter behind the MC, her boobs against his back)"
    show sc w3eowscooter c13
    s"Are you ready to start?"
    mc"I, I think so."
    show sc w3eowscooter c16
    s"Okay, this is similar to riding a bike, but once you get started, the scooter will do most of the work."
    s"It‚Äôs actually easier in a lot of ways."
    s"Now put the key in and set it to the on position."
    # (MC does this)"
    show sc w3eowscooter c18
    mc"Okay, I‚Äôve done that."
    show sc w3eowscooter c16
    s"All right, so to ignite it, just hold both brake levers with your left and right hands, and press the starter button to start the engine."
    s"As with most bikes, you will also need to give it a bit of gas, so just slightly turn the gas handle with your right palm."
