    s"Looks like you‚Äôre almost ready for take-off!"
    show sc w3eowscooter c14
    mc"What do I do next?"
    show sc w3eowscooter c16
    s"So you need to carefully release the brakes, and accelerate steadily by turning the gas handle slowly."
    s"And then you will start moving."
