    show sc w3eowscooter c28
    mc"([s_name]‚Äôs been telling me that she wouldn‚Äôt be able to do much without me here, but the truth is, I need to be around her just as much.)"
    mc"(I feel I could do anything when I‚Äôm with her.)"
    # (S puts her hands up in the air)"
    show sc w3eowscooter c30
    s"You‚Äôre a natural [y_name]! I knew you had it in you!"
