label lb_w3eow_21_connie_scooter:
    #     Week 3 (EOW) Scene 21 - Connie and the MC go into town on the scooter"
    scene sc w3eowconniesco c01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/01/Moped_running_effect.mp3" fadein 1.0
    mc"(Oh man‚Ä¶ This is great! I‚Äôve been missing out!)"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs a great way to spend time thinking about things.)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c02
    mc"(The main thought on my mind is what [s_name] was referring to when she said that we should do something together after the party tonight‚Ä¶)"
    mc"(Maybe what she meant is that we could have a celebratory drink together, or even sit up at the lighthouse tower and look at the ocean.)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c03
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ What if it‚Äôs neither of those things, and she wants to do more than what we did the other night?)"
    mc"(Surely that‚Äôs not what she meant, did she?)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c02
    mc"(I‚Äôm approaching the beach house.)"
    mc"(Even though I have to focus on Connie‚Äôs party today, it‚Äôs going to be hard not to think about what could happen later tonight‚Ä¶)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
