    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/00/soft_ocean_waves.mp3" fadein 1.0
    con"Hey [y_name]!"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c04
    mc"Hey Connie."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c07
    con"So I presume I'll be riding with you on your scooter back to the hotel?"
    mc"Yes. Is that okay?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c05
    con"Yes, of course."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c06
    con"But you know that I could‚Äôve just ordered an Uber to the hotel, right?"
    mc"Yes, but I think it would have been too much of a risk, just in case your Dad is monitoring your bookings or credit card transactions."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c09
    con"Oh, I didn‚Äôt think of that!"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c06
    mc"So as you can see, this is probably the smartest way to go about this."
    con"You‚Äôre right."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c07
    con"You know, it‚Äôs actually been a long while since I‚Äôve been on one of these things."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c06
    con"Is it yours?"
    mc"Uh, kind of. I borrowed it from a friend just while I‚Äôm here in town."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c04
    con"I see..."
    mc"Well, here‚Äôs a helmet for you, so uh, put that on, and then we can go."
    # (MC gives Connie a helmet)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c08
    con"Thanks."
    # (Connie has her helmet on)"
    con"Okay, I‚Äôm ready to go now."
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (Connie hops on the back of the scooter, her arms around Connie)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3eowconniesco c11
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/01/Moped_running_effect.mp3" fadein 1.0
    con"By the way, do you think we could stop off at the mall before we go to the hotel?"
    mc"Uh, sure, no problem. Do you mind if I ask why?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c10
    con"I need to pick up my dress for the party."
    con"I ordered it two weeks ago, and the store told me to pick it up today."
    mc"Sure, that should be okay."
    mc"(I‚Äôll have to message [s_name] to let her know that we‚Äôll be getting back a little late, but I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôll understand.)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (scene returns)"
    # (motor running sound FX)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c11
    con"So you were saying that the party preparations were going well?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c12
    mc"Oh yeah, you‚Äôre going to love what we‚Äôve done to the hotel pool area."
    mc"Your guests are going to be pleasantly surprised."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c13
    con"I love your confidence [y_name]. I can‚Äôt wait to see it!"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c12
    mc"[s_name] has ordered the balloons and decorations and they should arrive at the hotel before we return."
    mc"And your cake is going to be delivered this afternoon."
    con"You ordered me a cake?"
