    con"I still have some doubts about this idea though [y_name]."
    con"You know my Dad is bound to find out about this party eventually, right?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c12
    mc"[s_name] and I discussed this already."
    mc"We figure that as long as the party gets going, then there‚Äôs nothing he or his people can do about it."
    mc"You let us worry about any consequences afterward."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c11
    mc"(I can‚Äôt tell Connie that her father had the hotel investigated and that [s_name] and I were thrown in jail yesterday)."
    mc"(She doesn‚Äôt need to be told anything that may panic her.)"
