    mc"Sure thing."
    # (Connie walks off, MC watches her leave)"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c17
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ She sounds really happy. Hopefully, the party we‚Äôve put together lives up to her expectations.)"
    mc"(I wonder what her birthday dress looks like.)"
    mc"(I can only imagine it will be pretty special, not to mention expensive!)"
    mc"(Wait! Am I hearing myself right now? I‚Äôm carrying on like an over-excited school girl!)"
    mc"(Damn, I know it‚Äôs still early, but I could really do with a drink‚Ä¶)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3eowconniesco c22
    with dissolve
    # (Connie returns with a bag that contains her dress)"
    con"I‚Äôve got my dress!"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c21
    con"It looks as amazing as it did when I tried it on a couple of weeks back."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c19
    mc"Did you go with your Mom to buy it for today?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c18
    con"No, my family has no idea that I was in Sunshine Bay looking for my party dress."
    con"I went with one of my friends from school who was nice enough to drive me."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c21
    con"I wanted to surprise my parents but it looks like you and [s_name] will get to see me in it instead."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c18
    mc"Haha, well, we‚Äôd be very honoured to see that Connie."
    show sc w3eowconniesco c19
    con"So I was wondering‚Ä¶ Do you think I could drive the scooter back to the hotel?"
    mc"Oh, are you serious?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c21
    con"Sure, why not?"
    show sc w3eowconniesco c18
    con"I‚Äôve driven scooters before."
    con"It‚Äôs like riding a bicycle, once you get going, you just have to keep your balance to continue moving, right?"
    mc"Uh, yeah‚Ä¶"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ She sounds confident. But should I let Connie take us back to the hotel, or not?)"
