            con"This is awesome!! I need to buy myself one of these!"
            mc"They‚Äôre pretty amazing, hey?"
            con"Thanks for letting me drive [y_name]! It‚Äôs like getting the first of many birthday presents today!"
            mc"Haha! You‚Äôre welcome Connie."
